Ellise Chappell https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellise_Chappell 0 Ellise Chappell is an English actress. She is best known for her role as Morwenna Chynoweth in Poldark and is also known for her role as Jennifer Strange in The Last Dragonslayer. Ellise_Chappell is an_English_actress .
